dct_title_s: A Topographical Map of the Vicinity of Trenton, New Brunswick and Bordentown.
dct_description_sm: The historical New Jersey Geological Survey Atlas Sheets were scanned and georeferenced using ArcView 3.2a Image Analysis extension and ERDAS IMAGINE software packages. The georeferenced atlas sheets are in the New Jersey State Plane Coordinate System, NAD83.
